{"tid":2410959,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"15歲少年創下535場《FIFA 21》連勝記錄","createTime":"2021-02-17T04:17:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-17T04:19:00.000Z","uid":25345,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"119e3668ba8910ff3533da63a91db74a782a74e4","tid":2410959,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T04:17:37.000Z","msg":"[img]<a href=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0216%2Fd4bab421j00qom2680021c000u000gug.jpg&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0216%252Fd4bab421j00qom2680021c000u000gug.jpg%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&d=2uuoLuAEMU6cBVSXjgSp%2BcZCnWmYDHHppvVe94ioujI%3D&h=28c734b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0216%2Fd4bab421j00qom2680021c000u000gug.jpg&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg</a><br />\n[/img]<br />\n  15 歲的丹麥少年Anders Vejrgang 已經在《FIFA 21》 Ultimate Team 週末聯賽中連贏535 場對局，創下了全新的連勝紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nAnders Vejrgang<br />\n<br />\n  儘管因年齡問題，Vejrgang 尚不能參加EA 舉辦的《FIFA》官方賽事，但他是一位名副其實的天才玩家。早在12 歲時， Vejrgang 就在《FIFA 19》週末聯賽中達成了單週不敗的成績，而此次535 場《FIFA 21》對局連勝再次證明了他的超凡實力。目前Vejrgang 正效力於萊比錫紅牛俱樂部，且在國外Twitch 平台上擁有超過50 萬名粉絲。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n  略顯遺憾的是，Vejrgang 的連勝記錄在當地時間2 月14 日被打破。當時Vejrgang 遭遇了一位名為Black United 的對手，並最終不敵對方的猛烈進攻，遺憾輸掉比賽。不過賽后，紅牛俱樂部依然肯定了Vejrgang 的優異成績，並向他表示由衷的祝賀。"},{"pid":"1933b43622f2f75ca9a5f76eec669dca07699288","tid":2410959,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T04:18:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0216%2Fd4bab421j00qom2680021c000u000gug.jpg&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0216%252Fd4bab421j00qom2680021c000u000gug.jpg%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=bc880951&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b7d966ac5940545886cdaa29e3f46d3c28a70b1c","tid":2410959,"uid":189109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T04:19:00.000Z","msg":"電莖屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}